@startuml C5_search_integrated
title C5. 통합 검색 (이벤트+미팅)

actor User
participant "app-service" as SVC
database "PostgreSQL\n(Event/Meeting)" as PG

User -> SVC: GET /api/search?keyword=전시&target=events,meetings&tag=전시&size=10
SVC -> SVC: 파라미터 검증(허용 target/size)
SVC -> PG: SELECT events WHERE keyword/tag ...
SVC -> PG: SELECT meetings WHERE keyword/tag ...
SVC --> User: 200 OK {success:true, data:{events:[...], meetings:[...]}}
@enduml
